  <entry>
    <title>ABC449C-Comfortable-Distance</title>
    <link href="/2026/03/16/ABC449C-Comfortable-Distance/"/>
    <url>/2026/03/16/ABC449C-Comfortable-Distance/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="大意"><a href="#大意" class="headerlink" title="大意"></a>大意</h3><p>给定字符串 $S$ 和整数 $L, R$，求满足 $S_i&#x3D;S_j$ 且 $L \le j-i \le R$ 的下标对 $(i,j)$ 数量。</p><h3 id="思路"><a href="#思路" class="headerlink" title="思路"></a>思路</h3><p>暴力枚举 $O(N^2)$ 会超时。利用字符集仅 26 个的特性，将每种字符的下标单独提取。</p><p>问题转化为在多个有序数组中，统计差值在 $[L, R]$ 内的数对。对于每个右端点，合法左端点区间随其单调右移，使用双指针维护窗口 $[l, r)$，其中 $l$ 指向首个不小于 $cur-R$ 的位置，$r$ 指向首个大于 $cur-L$ 的位置，累加 $r-l$ 即可。</p><h3 id="Code"><a href="#Code" class="headerlink" title="Code"></a>Code</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">namespace</span> std;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">typedef</span> <span class="hljs-type">long</span> <span class="hljs-type">long</span> ll;<br>ll pos[<span class="hljs-number">500001</span>],L,R,n;<br>ll idx[<span class="hljs-number">27</span>],tmp[<span class="hljs-number">1001</span>];<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span>&#123;<br>cin&gt;&gt;n&gt;&gt;L&gt;&gt;R;<br>string s;<br>cin&gt;&gt;s;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(ll i=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;i&lt;<span class="hljs-number">26</span>;i++)idx[i]=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(ll i=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;i&lt;n;i++)&#123;<br>idx[s[i]-<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span><span class="hljs-number">+1</span>]++;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(ll i=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;i&lt;=<span class="hljs-number">26</span>;i++)idx[i]+=idx[i<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>];<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(ll i=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;i&lt;<span class="hljs-number">26</span>;i++)pos[idx[i]]=i;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(ll i=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;i&lt;n;i++)&#123;<br>ll c=s[i]-<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>;<br>pos[idx[c]+tmp[c]]=i;<br>tmp[c]++;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-type">long</span> <span class="hljs-type">long</span> t=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(ll c=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;c&lt;<span class="hljs-number">26</span>;c++)&#123;<br>ll s=idx[c];<br>ll e=idx[c<span class="hljs-number">+1</span>];<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(s&gt;=e)<span class="hljs-keyword">continue</span>;<br>ll l=s,r=s;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(ll j=s;j&lt;e;j++)&#123;<br>ll cur=pos[j];<br>ll minn=cur-R;<br>ll maxn=cur-L;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span>(l&lt;e&amp;&amp;pos[l]&lt;minn)l++;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span>(r&lt;e&amp;&amp;pos[r]&lt;=maxn)r++;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(r&gt;l)t+=(r-l);<br>&#125;<br>&#125;<br>cout&lt;&lt;t;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
